Detailed Description

cvmx_usbn::_dma0_outb_chn2

USBN_DMA0_OUTB_CHN2 = USBN's Outbound DMA for USB0 Channel2

Contains the starting address for use when USB0 reads from L2C via Channel2. Writing of this register sets the base address.
